External Knowledge: 
- "most prolific active authors" refers to users who have made the most posts and have their accounts in 'active' status; 
- "contribution" refers to a post; 
- "body of work" refers to the total number of posts made by a user; 
- "popularity" refers to the engagement count of a post.

sql:
SELECT first_name || ' ' || last_name AS full_name
FROM users
WHERE user_id = 1;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS report_count
FROM reported_users
WHERE reason = 'Harassment';
